:.START

:PAPERS: Thomson Corp. The Globe & Mail newspaper for November go begin dey send one special edition to select subscribers' facimile machine.

Di four page summary go reach readers wey dey outside Canada, or for Canadian, wey no dey for di day of publication.

For U.S., Confederation of a facsimile edition, and some oder newspapers dey reason on top di matter.

WHO: Michael T. Carr, wey dey advertise Playboy magazine, dem name am di Publisher of National Lampoon, and Heavy Metal Magazine wey dey succeed George Agoglia.

Di first oga wey change na Daniel Grodnik and Tim Matheson wey dey control National Lampoon Inc for March.

De dey find new editor for National Lampoon, and de wan sell Heavy Metal.

